OL,3,CMinister wants landlords investigated
OL,4,Cover illegal tenancy deposits
OL,6,FStates' figures show that between 2020
OL,7,Fand 2023, nearly a fifth of deposits
OL,8,Fsubmitted to the official Jersey
OL,9,Fscheme were not done within the agreed
OL,10,F30-day window.
OL,12,FThe real number of deposits not even
OL,13,Fincluded in the scheme is unknown.
OL,15,FThe independent initiative is designed
OL,16,Fto give tenants greater security and
OL,17,Fmake it easier for them to recover
OL,18,Ftheir money at the end of their lease.
