OL,3,CMinister wants landlords investigated
OL,4,Cover illegal tenancy deposits
OL,6,FIt also allows deposits to be kept
OL,7,Fsafe while an independent assessment
OL,8,Fis carried out if there are any
OL,9,Fdisagreements over damages or rental
OL,10,Fpayments.
OL,12,FITV News has been told that Attorney
OL,13,FGeneral Mark Temple KC, who is
OL,14,Fresponsible for these types of cases,
OL,15,Fallegedly said prosecuting landlords
OL,16,Ffor this offence does not meet the
OL,17,Fpublic interest threshold.
OL,19,FITV News has contacted the States
OL,20,FGreffe about this and did not
OL,21,Fimmediately receive a response.
