OL,3,CMinister wants landlords investigated
OL,4,Cover illegal tenancy deposits
OL,6,FDeputy Mezec wants a more proactive
OL,7,Fapproach, saying: "It's disappointing
OL,8,Fthat we have evidence lots of
OL,9,Flandlords aren't putting their
OL,10,Ftenant's deposits in the scheme within
OL,11,Fthe required time limit and not a lot
OL,12,Fhas been done to enforce that.
OL,14,F"There needs to be a look at why this
OL,15,Fhasn't been enforced properly because
OL,16,Fif it isn't, some people will question
OL,17,Fthe value of the scheme at all."
