OL,6,FA separate landlord licensing scheme
OL,7,Fwas recently rolled out in Jersey,
OL,8,Frequiring anyone receiving money for
OL,9,Frenting out rooms to buy a #60 permit
OL,10,Fper home and renew it every two years.
OL,12,FLatest figures show that rental income
OL,13,Ffrom private households makes up
OL,14,Faround 16% of the island's economy,
OL,15,Fonly surpassed by financial services
OL,16,Fthat covers 37.5%.
